com.aionemu.commons.scripting.scriptmanager
Class ScriptManager

java.lang.Object
  com.aionemu.commons.scripting.scriptmanager.ScriptManager

public class ScriptManager
extends java.lang.Object

Class that represents managers of script contexes. It loads, reloads and unload script contexes. In the future it may be extended to support programatic manipulation of contexes, but for now it's not needed.
Example: 

      ScriptManager sm = new ScriptManager();
      sm.load(new File("st/contexts.xml"));
      ...
      sm.shutdown();
ScriptContext object creation listener can be added by using com.aionemu.commons.scripting.scriptmanager.listener.ContextCreationListener ScriptContext object reload listener can be added by using com.aionemu.commons.scripting.scriptmanager.listener.ContextReloadListener ScriptManager reload listener can be added by using com.aionemu.commons.scripting.scriptmanager.listener.ReloadListener

Author:
SoulKeeper, Aquanox
